# Conclusion

This project demonstrates a secure employee onboarding workflow using AWS cloud services.

By combining:

- Amazon S3
- AWS KMS
- AWS Secrets Manager
- Flask

the solution provides secure document storage, credential management, encryption, and employee record management while following AWS security best practices.
